%% Session Processing Pipeline
flowchart TD
    A[Upload or Record Session Clip] --> B[Validate File Type, Size, Duration]
    B -->|Valid| C[Store Media in Cloud Storage]
    B -->|Invalid| X[Return Validation Error]

    C --> D[Create LearningSession Record<br/>Status: Uploaded]
    D --> E[Publish Pub/Sub Event<br/>SessionUploaded]
    E --> F[Cloud Run Worker Starts Processing]

    F --> G{Media Type?}
    G -->|Video| H[Extract Audio with FFmpeg]
    G -->|Audio| I[Use Uploaded Audio]

    H --> J[Store Extracted Audio<br/>Cloud Storage]
    I --> K[Call Speech-to-Text]
    J --> K

    K --> L[Store Transcript Segments<br/>Cloud SQL]
    L --> M[Call Vertex AI Gemini<br/>Transcript Analysis]
    M --> N[Generate Learning Signals]

    N --> O{Video Analysis Enabled?}
    O -->|Yes| P[Call Video Intelligence API<br/>or Custom Vision Worker]
    O -->|No| Q[Skip Visual Signals]

    P --> R[Store Visual Signals]
    Q --> S[Calculate Session Metrics]
    R --> S

    S --> T[Generate Summary + Recommendations<br/>Vertex AI Gemini]
    T --> U[Persist Metrics, Insights, Recommendations]
    U --> V[Update Status: Completed]
    V --> W[Dashboard Displays Results]

    F -->|Failure| Z[Update Status: Failed<br/>Store Error Reason]
    K -->|Failure| Z
    M -->|Failure| Z
    T -->|Failure| Z
